Requirements:

For ttusb_dec_reset, you will need libusb.

Building:

Simply type
$ make

Build options
  static=1		- Build all applications statically.
  V=1			- Verbose output during build.
  ttusb_dec_reset=1	- Build the optional ttusb_dec_reset.

Installing:

$ make install
installs libraries and utils to /usr/[bin,include,lib]

$ make install prefix=<path>
installs libraries and utils to <path>/[bin,include,lib]
